            </rs>.</p>
               <p>SECOND COUNT for receiving into his possession a promissory note of the governor and company of the bank of England, value 300 l. another note, value 200 l. a ten pound bank note, and a five pound bank note, and that he afterwards did embezzle and steal the same.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18100718-42-person441">
                  WILLIAM 
                  REECE
               <interp inst="t18100718-42-person441" type="surname" value="REECE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18100718-42-person441" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18100718-42-person441" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a <rs id="t18100718-42-viclabel252" type="occupation">broker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18100718-42-victim434 t18100718-42-viclabel252"></join>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18100718-42-victim436 t18100718-42-viclabel252"></join>
